snippet.textDisplay: We need transparency from all mass media. Give specific names of people who reported this. Do thorough research where information comes from. All virology laboratory researchers should be held liable for any kind of experiment including its president and director. If anything goes south, then sandbox the area affected and whoever is infected should be isolated for full investigation.
